Package: autofileIO
Title: Automated File and Database I/O for R
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ankit Akash", "Kalita", email = "ankitakashkalita2002@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: A smart and flexible I/O package that automatically detects
    file types and database connections, then applies the appropriate read
    and write functions.
